output.analysis:
Let me analyze this post according to the given criteria:
1. CMF Number: No CMF number is present, but this isn't decisive by itself.
2. Direct Reference to Candidate: Yes, explicitly mentions "George Simion" and uses hashtags #georgesimionpresedinte, who is a registered presidential candidate.
3. Addresses Wide Population: Yes - It's a paid advertisement on Facebook and Instagram - Targets a large audience (500,001-1,000,000 people) - Already reached 5,000-5,999 impressions - Announces a public march in Suceava
4. Electoral Objective: Yes - Uses hashtags like #alegeri2024 #alegeri - Explicitly promotes "George Simion președinte" - Organizing a support march specifically for the candidate - Clear campaign activity
5. Journalism: No - This is not journalistic content - It's a call to action for a political march - Promotes a specific candidate
6. Personal Opinion: No - This is an organized political activity - Paid advertisement by a company (SC VIDEO DANCRYS-STUDIO SRL) - Clear campaign messaging
This post constitutes electoral propaganda as it meets all criteria under Article 36(7) and is being run after the conclusion of the presidential campaign period.

conclusion.electoral-propaganda-analysis: This is clearly electoral propaganda because: - Directly promotes a presidential candidate - Organized political activity (march) - Paid advertisement reaching large audiences - Uses explicit campaign hashtags - Commercial entity paying for political promotion
conclusion.message-for-police: SC VIDEO DANCRYS-STUDIO SRL, pentru incalcarea articolului 55 t) din Legea 370/2004, prin difuzarea de materiale de propagandă electorală după încheierea perioadei de campanie, constând într-o postare plătită pe Facebook și Instagram (ID: 1146734783545268) care promovează direct candidatul GEORGE-NICOLAE SIMION prin organizarea unui marș de susținere și utilizarea hashtag-urilor de campanie (#georgesimionpresedinte). Postarea a fost activă după ora 18:00 pe 23.11.2024, atingând între 5.000 și 5.999 de afișări, având un impact electoral direct prin mobilizarea populației într-o acțiune politică explicită de susținere a unui candidat la președinție.
